N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 182.2 - Procedure

State Regulations

Prior to action by the committee, examination shall be
made, upon receipt of a request for a change in name, of printed materials, such as maps, gazetteers, atlases and local histories, and of local usage; and
inquiries shall be made concerning endorsement by local public authorities, local press and individuals. Notes
